<h2>Proust in der Konstellation der Moderne. Proust dans la constellation des modernes (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2121'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
